title: PREVIEW: Big 12 Men's Golf Championship - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: PREVIEW: Big 12 Men's Golf Championship - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: No. 5 Texas Tech is set to compete in the 2022 Big 12 Men's Golf Championship next week at the Whispering Pines Golf Club in Trinity, Texas. The Red Raiders will be represented at the 25th annual postseason tournament by Ludvig Aberg, Baard Skogen, Calum Scott, Andy Lopez, Sandy Scott and Carl Didrik Meen Fosaas.
